formThreeBId.notesToCertificate: In Form 3 (Annexure), whereever Date of agreement of sale is not available, we have mentioned date of execution of sale deed in favour of customer.We have relied upon the estimates given by the management in case of costs other than construction  cost.The preparation of the accompanying Statement is the responsibility of the Management of the Company. This responsibility includes designing, implementing and maintaining internal control relevant to the preparation and presentation of the Statement, and applying an appropriate basis of preparation; and making estimates that are reasonable in the circumstances.Cost of Land is considered as per the sale deed of Land. Land cost is not indexed. Carpet Area of the unit, Exclusive Balcony Area of the unit, and No of parkings and KYC Details of unit holders are taken as provided by the management. The certificate is addressed to and provided to the promoters of the project solely for the purpose to enable comply with requirement of RERA , and should not be used by any other person or for any other purpose. Accordingly, we do not accept or assume any liability or any duty of care for any other purpose or to any other person to whom this certificate is shown or into whose hands it may come without our prior consent in writing. Booking Deposits are taken under the head sundry debtors We have not audited books of accounts of the entity , the certificate is prepared basis the data provided to us. As informed to us by the promoter there was no unused material lying in stock as on the date of certification. Loan disbursal and repayment amount includes interest on loan accrued and paid. in the loan schedule there are certain payments which are paid to the creditors directly from the loan account. Promoter has opened new rera a/c with Axis Bank Rera Account No:-921020000409630- and also routing the amounts in this account but the same is not updated with RERA bank. We have taken withdrawl amount as per the total receipt of the booking deposit reduced by the closing bank balance available in RERA Bank Account.
